data.description: Nestled in the heart of Norris Lake's enchanting community in Snellville, this fully renovated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom ranch-style home weaves a tale of comfort, privacy, and modern living. As you stroll up the welcoming 3-car driveway, your front porch beckons, offering a perfect spot for evening drinks and enchanting views of the lake.    Step inside and discover a split floorplan that's a symphony of comfort and seclusion. The master bedroom, tucked away on one side of the home, reveals its spacious layout with a charming sitting areaCoan oasis for unwinding, reading a book, or simply soaking in the serene lake views. A magical door beckons, leading to the backyard and your private deck, where morning coffee and stargazing adventures await. The dining room, set for six, serves as the stage for family feasts and gatherings, while the separate living room provides a canvas for relaxation and entertainment, ensuring everyone finds their own slice of paradise.    But that's just the beginning of this whimsical journey! In the Norris Lake community, excitement and leisure take center stage. Dive into the community pool's refreshing waters, bask on the sandy shores of the community beach, or engage in spirited matches on the on-site tennis courts. The 92-acre lake, welcoming motorboats, promises endless aquatic adventuresCofrom fishing to thrilling water sports. Join the community's vibrant spirit with monthly events that weave neighbors into lifelong friends, and for the green-thumbed souls, the community garden is an enchanting sanctuary. With the world at your fingertips, Atlanta (30-45 minutes), Decatur (30 minutes), Lawrenceville (30 minutes), and shopping centers (just 15 minutes away) are all within easy reach. At 955 Lake Drive, Norris Lake invites you not only into a beautifully renovated home but also a vibrant community where the joys of lakeside living come to life. Embrace tranquility and boundless recreation in this extraordinary setting. Don't let this storybook opportunity slip awayCoschedule a showing today!
